  "text": "We present selected, representative results from a broader experimental study. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] Overall, the experiments show that CLA achieves operations performance close to the uncompressed case while yielding substantially better compression ratios than lightweight general-purpose compression. Therefore, CLA provides large end-to-end performance improvements when uncompressed or lightweight-compressed matrices do not fit into aggregate cluster memory.",
